      "type": "html",
      "text": "<i>After a year of diligent effort, a group of nearly 50 dedicated users and developers are proud to release [[Wiki Creole]] 1.0. Creole is designed to be a common wiki markup language which augments existing markup to enable wiki users to transfer content seamlessly across wikis, a boon to novice and expert users alike.</i>",
      "id": "9bef2ae011551d73bef4f1b88c8d08b1"
